Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Read Me :",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\nThis model accompanies the USITC report, ",
 StyleBox["Economic Impact of Section 232 and 301 Tariffs on U.S. Industries,",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " Inv. 332-591. The report includes a quantitative analysis of the economic \
impact of section 232 tariffs on U.S. prices, production and imports. The \
model inputs (ORANGE-shaded cells) include elasticities that describe \
responsiveness to price changes, and domestic production and imports data. \
Data sources are listed in the cell above the data input. The model inputs \
include the effects of the 232 tariffs. Then, the model simulation estimates \
what prices and quantities would have looked like if section 232 tariffs were \
not in place. Outputs are in the GREEN-shaded cells. The white cells are \
intermediate calculations. \n\nNote: NAICS 336300 is an aggregate of NAICS \
336330 and NAICS 336340."
}], "Text",
