Steel Flat Products from Australia, Brazil, Japan, Korea, the Netherlands, \
Turkey, and the United Kingdom, July 2016; USITC, Cold-Rolled Steel Flat \
Products from China and Japan, July 2016; Bown and Russ, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Biden and Europe Remove Trump\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Steel \
