industry analysts as necessary. For more information on the steps taken to \
calculate these values, see Appendix F of the report.\nU.S. Census Bureau, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Annual Survey of Manufactures,\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] \
accessed October 17, 2022. BEA, \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Input-Output Accounts \
